            "step_number" : 2,
            "step_description" : "In a large frying pan, heat the olive oil on a low-medium heat and saut√© the onion for 2 minutes until softened. Add the sugar and balsamic vinegar. Cook for a further 3 minutes or until fully soft."
        },
        {
            "step_number" : 3,
            "step_description" : "Add in the garlic and courgette. Fry for 10 minutes on a medium heat, until the vegetables are cooked. Add a little more olive oil or a splash of water if the pan gets dry."
        },
        {
            "step_number" : 4,
            "step_description" : "In a large bowl, add the cooked cous cous, the turmeric, chickpeas and stir in the fried vegetables. Mix well and season with salt and pepper."
        },
        {
